Package hu.bme.mit.theta.xcfa.analysis.portfolio.common

Class CegarConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.bme.mit.theta.xcfa.analysis.portfolio.common.CegarConfiguration
  • public class CegarConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a wrapper and extension to the XcfaConfig class It stores and is capable of returning the information an XcfaConfig stores, but it also stores information on the solvers used, if arg-cex check is used and if the solver is validated
